sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Operator as OGX K8s Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Kustomize as Embedded Kustomize<br/>Engine
    participant OGXPod as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Remote Provider<br/>(vLLM/OpenAI/Azure/etc.)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(PGVector/Milvus/Qdrant)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>HTTPS/9443, K8s API mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/rejected

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (OGXServer changed)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from<br/>base templates + CR spec
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, NP, PVC, HPA, PDB)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service, NetworkPolicy,<br/>PVC, HPA, PDB, Ingress, ConfigMap
    Operator->>OGXPod: GET /v1/providers, /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321, health check
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Provider info, version
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: OGX Server Inference Request

    User->>OGXPod: POST /v1/inference<br/>HTTP or HTTPS/{port}<br/>Application-level auth
    OGXPod->>Provider: Forward to remote provider<br/>HTTPS/443, API key / IAM credentials
    Provider-->>OGXPod: Inference response
    OGXPod->>VectorDB: Vector I/O query<br/>TCP, password/token auth
    VectorDB-->>OGXPod: Vector results
    OGXPod->>S3: File storage operations<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS credentials
    S3-->>OGXPod: File data
    OGXPod-->>User: Inference response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Legacy Adoption Migration

    User->>K8sAPI: Create OGXServer CR with<br/>adoption annotations<br/>(ogx.io/adopt-storage,<br/>ogx.io/adopt-networking)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (OGXServer with adoption)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale legacy LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Deployment to 0 replicas
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Wait for legacy pods to terminate
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Relabel PVCs, update Service selectors,<br/>transfer Ingress ownership
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Record adoption timestamps<br/>in OGXServer annotations
